== Overview ==
Name after the god of Thunder, this weapon acts no differently. This weapon packs quite a punch and can devastate groups of enemies in a single blast. Quite literally 'Thor' will shake its target to the core.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Thor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
